# TRAILING SLASH REDIRECT
# ============================================
# /tools/           /tools                       301!
# /blog/            /blog                        301!

# ============================================
# CANONICAL REDIRECTS
# ============================================
# Redirect www to non-www (or vice versa) - handled by Cloudflare DNS

# ============================================
# AFFILIATE/TRACKING PARAMETER CLEANUP
# ============================================
# Remove tracking parameters but keep the page
